  "detailed_description": "A fusion of roguelikes and auto-battlers like never before seen. Recruit a party of mysterious heroes, navigate deadly lands, collect an arsenal of magical items, and vanquish a new evil threatening the realm!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><li><strong><i>Party-Based Strategy</i></strong>: Select from a pool of unique heroes, each with skills which inspire vastly different strategies and customization. Position your heroes on the battlefield to influence the outcome of battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Explore Dynamic Terrain</i></strong>: Each playthrough provides a new journey, changing not only your path, but the bosses you must conquer. Freely move between 3 subareas in each act, rewarding those with the knowledge of where their party can flourish, and where it will falter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Loot!</i></strong>: Collect ancient and magical items which augment your party's stats and abilities. Should your Wildmage be a glass cannon, or a front line bruiser? The decision is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Prestige!</i></strong>: After your first victory, heroes will begin growing a cosmetic aura as they conquer the 20 additional Corruption modifiers.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Astronarch comes with:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>21 Unique and mysterious heroes to unlock.<br></li><li>130+ Mystical items for your arsenal.<br></li><li>100+ Combat encounters, including 11 elite enemies and 12 bosses.<br></li><li>30+ Intriguing map events to be discovered.<br></li><li>3 Acts containing 3 subareas, each with different enemies and terrain.<br></li><li>20 Devious corruption levels to conquer following your first victory.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "A fusion of roguelikes and auto-battlers like never before seen. Recruit a party of mysterious heroes, navigate deadly lands, collect an arsenal of magical items, and vanquish a new evil threatening the realm!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d357b2ccae90d379bfcb0ec25b91f6a3.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><li><strong><i>Party-Based Strategy</i></strong>: Select from a pool of unique heroes, each with skills which inspire vastly different strategies and customization. Position your heroes on the battlefield to influence the outcome of battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/db3ea3f4edac85715d9aa14a8bcfce2c.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Explore Dynamic Terrain</i></strong>: Each playthrough provides a new journey, changing not only your path, but the bosses you must conquer. Freely move between 3 subareas in each act, rewarding those with the knowledge of where their party can flourish, and where it will falter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/34e72ee9f9d37104f099f5c8c06e016e.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Loot!</i></strong>: Collect ancient and magical items which augment your party's stats and abilities. Should your Wildmage be a glass cannon, or a front line bruiser? The decision is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.poster.avif?t=1758888897\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.webm?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234940/extras/d8f14d4a53fdaf16e91d13585a00ea21.mp4?t=1758888897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong><i>Prestige!</i></strong>: After your first victory, heroes will begin growing a cosmetic aura as they conquer the 20 additional Corruption modifiers.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Astronarch comes with:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>21 Unique and mysterious heroes to unlock.<br></li><li>130+ Mystical items for your arsenal.<br></li><li>100+ Combat encounters, including 11 elite enemies and 12 bosses.<br></li><li>30+ Intriguing map events to be discovered.<br></li><li>3 Acts containing 3 subareas, each with different enemies and terrain.<br></li><li>20 Devious corruption levels to conquer following your first victory.</li></ul>",
